cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI 

This paper deals with depth estimation and regularization using a graph-based approach, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of optimization and machine learning algorithms also suggests a possible fit with machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the estimation of normals, which is a common task in computer graphics (cs.GR).
